            "description": "<main class=\"c1tt5pk2\" id=\"article-container\" style=\"--c1tt5pk2-0:20px\"><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>康霈*(<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:6919:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/6919\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">6919-TW</a>)19日11:59下跌19.5元，股價跌停報176.5元，委買8,368張、委賣200張，成交40,727張。</p></section><p></p><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>主要業務為專精於醫美與慢性發炎疾病領域的新藥開發。健康食品研發。</p></section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>康霈*(<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:6919:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/6919\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">6919-TW</a>)近5日股價下跌5.31%，集中市場<a href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/index/TWS/TSE01\">加權指數</a>上漲2.2%，短期股價無明顯表現。</p></section><section><p><em>近5日籌碼</em></p></section><!--$--><!--/$--><section style=\"margin-top:20px\"><ul> <li>三大法人合計買賣超：+5,823 張</li> <li>外資買賣超：+6,022 張</li> <li>投信買賣超：-154 張</li> <li>自營商買賣超：-45 張</li> </ul></section></main>",
